title: IOWAck AF, Dunkaroo Strategies 2.5.20
itunes:title: IOWAck AF, Dunkaroo Strategies 2.5.20
description:
In episode 563, Jack and Miles are joined by The Greatest podcast co-host Megan Gailey to discuss the Iowa caucus, Trump supporters explanations for why he shouldn't be impeached, Wendy's breakfast, the return of Dunkaroos, 2020 movies that may influence the election, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Abolish the Iowa Caucus
  2. Iowa Might Have Screwed Up The Whole Nomination Process
  3. Iowa caucuses: Attendee drops, breaks ‘concealed bottle of wine’
  4. How unpopular is Donald Trump?
  5. Wendy's promises to end the era of stale fast-food breakfast on March 2
  6. Dunkaroos are coming back—what else do you need to know?
  7. Spielberg’s Lincoln holds a mirror up to Barack Obama
  8. Steven Spielberg's 'West Side Story' Movie Unveils A Cool First Look
  9. Meet the Cast of the James Comey Miniseries From CBS TV Studios
  10. Donald Trump, Hillary Clinton influenced 'The Purge: Election Year'
  11. Looks Like The Candyman Reboot Is Taking The Character To New Places
  12. Mulan 2020
  13. Mike Pence: Disney's Mulan is 'mischievous liberal propaganda'
  14. WATCH: Westside Gunn X Conway - Fendi Seats
